@startuml
title FlowJS State Diagram (Part 2: Rendering & Runtime)


ReadyToRender --> Rendering : start()

state Rendering {
  [*] --> UpdateLoop
  UpdateLoop --> UpdateLODs : Each frame
  UpdateLODs --> RenderFrame
  RenderFrame --> UpdateLoop
}

Rendering --> Stopped : stop()
Stopped --> Rendering : start()
Rendering --> [*] : dispose()

@enduml
